{
  "stem": "12462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, I think Fritzsche could explain a lot of this, if you're willing to take the explanations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it will improve what you know about the defendant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm-- we're perfectly willing to tell you this in advance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, well, prove it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I would ask questions, through him, of Fritzsche, whom I never interrogated directly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they would bring me back, in German, Fritzsche's response.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd have them translated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, we made a 20-page affidavit, and which he then signed, just after the Christmas holidays, in 1945.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that became the principal document that, really, I relied upon in my presentation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in there, it was very plain that he said, 'I accuse the international, Bolshevistic, Jewish, capitalist, clique across the world of having caused this war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they are the ones who are committing atrocities,' and all this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we tried to do is accuse him-- not that he was telling untruths, but that he was supporting a vicious regime, which was killing people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no proof that he had received documents concerning the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had been in Russia at the time that the Einsatzgruppen were killing people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'd been attached for [CLEARS THROAT] some six months or so, after the Russians-- after the Soviet Union had been invaded, to a propaganda unit of one of the armies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And no one can believe, in his right mind, that that doesn't mean that he knew what the-- was going on, in the terms of killing a million people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had no proof of it and never could find a witness who could say, we know that Fritzsche knew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a matter of inference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the tribunal found him not guilty.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
